# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ecommerce Factory — marketing site environment.
#
# The marketing site can run as a standalone static landing page. Set these
# public URLs when you want the CTAs to open the deployed engine/admin/demo apps.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Example (optional):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ANALYTICS_ID=

# Deployed engine storefront/admin.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENGINE_URL=https://your-engine.example.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENGINE_ADMIN_URL=https://your-engine.example.com/admin/dashboard

# Optional explicit live demo URLs. Use these when each demo has a separate
# domain, subdomain, or Cloudflare route.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEMO_MAISON_NOIR_URL=https://maison-noir.your-engine.example.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEMO_LUMEN_URL=https://lumen.your-engine.example.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEMO_TERRA_ASH_URL=https://terra-ash.your-engine.example.com
